    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s been super well-loved? I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and she\u2019s still got so much life left in her! It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been perfect for getting around town and the occasional road trip. It runs like a charm and is totally ready for its next adventure with a new owner. If you want a dependable car that won't let you down, come take a look! I'm super easy to talk to, so feel free to reach out with any questions!",
