    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L straight-six engine and a desirable 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. This example is mechanically sorted with documented VANOS servicing and a reinforced rear subframe to ensure chassis rigidity under lateral load. The naturally aspirated powerplant maintains excellent compression, delivering 333 hp through its individual throttle bodies to the factory limited-slip differential. Recent service includes a cooling system refresh and an inspection of the rod bearings. While the exterior shows minor stone chipping consistent with use, the performance envelope remains sharp, offering the tactile steering and balanced weight distribution synonymous with the M-division's peak era.",
