    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2017 Porsche Macan S in Volcano Grey Metallic. This vehicle strikes a perfect balance between a spirited driver and a reliable daily companion. The exterior retains a deep, mirror-like shine, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small, professional touch-up on the rear passenger door\u2014standard for a car that has been enjoyed on the open road. Inside, the Agate Grey leather interior is in excellent shape; the bolsters show only slight softening, and the dashboard is free of any sun damage or cracks. All electronics, from the heated seats to the premium Bose surround system, function perfectly. Mechanically, this Macan is top-tier. It has a comprehensive service history with its most recent major interval completed just 3,000 miles ago, including fresh fluids and a multi-point inspection. The 3.0L V6 biturbo engine delivers smooth, consistent power, and the PDK transmission remains lightning-fast. It currently sits on N-spec Pirelli Scorpion Verde tires with approximately 70% tread life remaining. This is a turnkey luxury SUV for a buyer who values a documented history and mechanical integrity over a 'showroom-only' status.",
      "price": 36500.0,
